data.description: Welcome Home to this beautiful home in LaMarche Place Villas.  Walk in to an open kitchen, dining and living room with vaulted ceiling and corner fireplace.  Beautiful kitchen with granite countertops.  Primary bedroom is on the main level with a luxurious bathroom.  Upstairs are 3 additional bedrooms and bathroom, with plenty of closet space and walk in attic access.  Tankless HWH, low E windows. Through the living room access your covered porch and extended deck to enjoy your morning coffee!  Don Roberts Elementary and Pinnacle View Middle School.  Location is fantastic!  Schedule your showing today!!  Agents see Remarks! Back on Market due to no fault of the seller!!
